# Discoverable universes for the Open Universe start-screen "Universe" dropdown.
# Each label registers a universe (type: universe/<key>) naming its clans and
# narrative AMD files. Add more universes by adding more labels here.

=== universe_default
metadata:``` yaml
type: universe/default
key: default
display: Default
clans: clans.amd
narrative: narrative.amd
```
    ->END
